<h1 class='page-title'>Barbarian</h1>
<p>
<a class='editPageContent' href='javascript:void(0);'>Edit Page Content</a>
</p>
<div data-pageid='5197' id='pagecontent'>As a Barbarian, you gain the following class features:<br><br><a name="h-Hit%20Points"></a><h2>Hit Points</h2>
<strong>Hit Dice</strong>: 1d12 per barbarian level<br><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level</strong>: 12 + your <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Ability%20Scores#h-Constitution">Constitution</a> modifier<br><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels</strong>: 1d12 (or 7) + your <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Ability%20Scores#h-Constitution">Constitution</a> modifier per barbarian level after 1st<br><br><a name="h-Proficiencies"></a><h2>Proficiencies</h2>
<strong><a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Armor#h-Armor">Armor</a></strong>: <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Armor#h-Light%20Armor">Light Armor</a>, <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Armor#h-Medium%20Armor">Medium Armor</a>, shields Weapons: Simple <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Weapons#h-Weapons">Weapons</a>, martial <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Weapons#h-Weapons">Weapons</a> Tools: None<br><strong>Saving Throws</strong>: <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Ability%20Scores#h-Strength">Strength</a>, <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Ability%20Scores#h-Constitution">Constitution</a><br><strong>Skills</strong>: Choose two from Animal Handling, Athletics, Intimidation, Nature, Perception, and Survival<br><br><a name="h-Equipment"></a><h2><a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Equipment#h-Equipment">Equipment</a></h2>You start with the following <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Equipment#h-Equipment">Equipment</a>, in addition to the <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Equipment#h-Equipment">Equipment</a> granted by your background:<br><ul>
<li>(<em>a</em>) a <a class="autolink" href="/compendium/dnd5e/Greataxe#h-Greataxe">Greataxe</a> or (<em>b</em>) any martial melee weapon</li>
<li>(<em>a</em>) two handaxes or (<em>b</em>) any simple weapon</li>
<li>An explorer’s pack and four javelins</li>
</ul>
